{"tid":1426540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持沒有談判對象","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:38:36.000Z","uid":61672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52e55a731eaecc2159f0837fcffc69c2e25dac95","tid":1426540,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"其實政府每日都出好多新聞稿，點解你唔知因為冇人提，政府記者會都一樣，你冷處理冇人關注由佢沈底，佢就造唔到輿論，但攪個民間記者會仲endorses 返政府記者會，民間記者會回應政府，攪攪下會好似談判，比政府拖住個鼻子走，話你港獨否認港獨，話你外國勢力，你否認有外國勢力，話你放火，咁你點否認呢？ 只要當政府係個痴線佬係條街度自言自語，正常人唔會同個痴線佬嗌交，因為就會變左有兩個痴線佬係度嘈架啦<br />\n<br />\n所以做個杯葛記者會運動，而不是攪民間記者會，不收看不分亨不評論不回應不做反應彈，當政府用好多錢去宣傳一套愛國電影，又周街派飛，我地可以杯葛佢唔入場等佢零票房。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲圍爐取暖就他去，返正佢地都係睇cctvb 同時聞香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10109573445909476&amp;id=2543651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10109573445909476%26id%3D2543651&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=e1f9ef3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10109573445909476&amp;id=2543651</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集中火力游擊，流水抗爭<br />\n沒有代表 沒有大台<br />\n杯葛政府記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0bf10834fbe3b80283dac444d793224cab4729","tid":1426540,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"4753ed849f1342a4be499d5dbdeb87a88e0e003f","tid":1426540,"uid":78767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"DLLM，你一係就睇唔通民間記者會對呢次革命嘅重要性，一係就係喺度分化，是但揀樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk